gsonpath

Enum GsonPathFieldNamingPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GsonPathFieldNamingPolicy>
      • gsonpath.GsonPathFieldNamingPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GsonPathFieldNamingPolicy>

    public enum GsonPathFieldNamingPolicy
extends java.lang.Enum<GsonPathFieldNamingPolicy>
    Provides the exact same functionality as the Gson FieldNamingPolicy enum, however this class was created to provide an easy way to inherit a default value if required by using the IDENTITY_OR_INHERIT_DEFAULT_IF_AVAILABLE variation of the IDENTITY value.
